Pil pivo, lovil ribe v jezeru.

00:49:27.960 --> 00:49:31.158
Ti veliko, prečudovito blato!

00:49:31.159 --> 00:49:33.279
35 odstotkov.

00:49:33.280 --> 00:49:34.598
Drži se, srček!

00:49:34.599 --> 00:49:36.198
Gremo domov!
